      "instruction": "<p>While the fish is cooking, roughly dice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Chop <strong>half</strong> your <strong>cucumber</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) into small, bite-sized pieces and chop your <strong>parsley</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Add the <strong>diced tomato</strong>, <strong>chopped cucumber </strong>and <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>chopped parsley</strong> to a bowl with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>ground sumac </strong>(save the rest for later!),<strong> </strong>a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>, then give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>Greek-style salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
